/wiki/Grigory_Misutin: Grigory Misutin ( born 29 December 1970 ) is a Ukrainian artistic gymnast , formerly representing the Soviet Union and the Unified Team .
/wiki/Li_Jing_(gymnast): Li Jing ( Chinese : 李敬 ; born February 23 , 1970 ) is a Chinese gymnast , world champion and Olympic medalist . He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona where he received silver medals in rings , in parallel bars , and in team combined exercises .
/wiki/Igor_Korobchinsky: Ihor Korobchynskyi ( Ukrainian : Коробчинський Ігор Олексійович ; born 16 August 1969 ) is a former gymnast that represented the Soviet Union , the Commonwealth of Independent States and Ukraine . In 2016 , he was inducted in the International Gymnastics Hall of Fame .
/wiki/Johan_Jonasson: Johan Jonasson ( born 9 October 1966 ) is a Swedish gymnast . He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics , the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics .
/wiki/Yukio_Iketani: Yukio Iketani ( 池谷 幸雄 , Iketani Yukio , born September 26 , 1970 ) is a Japanese gymnast and Olympic medalist .
/wiki/Curtis_Hibbert: Curtis Mayfield Hibbert ( born 2 September 1966 ) is a police constable and Canadian Olympian . He is the first Canadian and first person of colour to win World Championship medals in gymnastics . With five golds , Hibbert is the most successful gymnast in history in a single Commonwealth Games .
/wiki/Rob_Doyle: Rob Doyle ( born 10 February 1964 ) is an Austrian ice hockey player . He competed in the men 's tournament at the 1994 Winter Olympics .
/wiki/Li_Chunyang: Li Chunyang ( born 2 February 1968 ) is a Chinese former gymnast who competed in the 1988 Summer Olympics and in the 1992 Summer Olympics . He was the 1989 and 1991 world champion on horizontal bar .
/wiki/Daisuke_Nishikawa: Daisuke Nishikawa ( born 2 June 1970 ) is a retired Japanese gymnast who competed in the 1988 Summer Olympics and in the 1992 Summer Olympics .
